    "unsozial ist drin. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.440", 
   "id": "s000093", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Soziale Politik gibt es ausschlie\u00dflich mit der AfD."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.480", 
   "id": "s000094", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich trage Ihnen auch sehr gerne vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.600", 
   "id": "s000095", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wir das regeln wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.040", 
   "id": "s000096", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben ja sicherlich die Drucksache gelesen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.080", 
   "id": "s000097", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ansonsten lade ich Sie ein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.680", 
   "id": "s000098", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Seite drei des Gesetzentwurfs aufzuschlagen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.000", 
   "id": "s000099", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sagen n\u00e4mlich Folgendes: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.000", 
   "id": "s000100", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese ganze Unterscheidung zwischen Sachgrund und sachgrundlos hat keinen besonderen Sinn; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.040", 
   "id": "s000101", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn das IAB hat festgestellt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.000", 
   "id": "s000102", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "93\u00a0Prozent der befristeten Arbeitsverh\u00e4ltnisse haben tats\u00e4chlich einen gedanklichen Hintergrund, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.480", 
   "id": "s000103", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Sinn macht; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.840", 
   "id": "s000104", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie sind sachlich befristet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.240", 
   "id": "s000105", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das steht nicht immer drauf; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.800", 
   "id": "s000106", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
