   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.640", 
   "id": "s000107", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann kann der Arbeitnehmer Sie als Arbeitgeber vor dem Arbeitsgericht verklagen und gegebenenfalls eine Entfristung des Arbeitsverh\u00e4ltnisses feststellen lassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.760", 
   "id": "s000108", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen steht es nicht im Arbeitsvertrag; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.600", 
   "id": "s000109", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber es gibt trotzdem einen Grund."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.560", 
   "id": "s000110", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.800", 
   "id": "s000111", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
