   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.920", 
   "id": "s000112", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie uns die Regeln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.480", 
   "id": "s000113", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die bisher f\u00fcr die sachgrundlose Befristung galten\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.320", 
   "id": "s000114", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "maximal 24\u00a0Monate mit maximal drei Verl\u00e4ngerungen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.920", 
   "id": "s000115", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verallgemeinern und sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.760", 
   "id": "s000116", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.680", 
   "id": "s000117", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir brauchen Befristungen f\u00fcr die Flexibilit\u00e4t der Arbeitgeber. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.880", 
   "id": "s000118", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist wichtig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.120", 
   "id": "s000119", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben schon jetzt 1,7\u00a0Milliarden \u00dcberstunden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.680", 
   "id": "s000120", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir wollen nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.640", 
   "id": "s000121", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es mehr werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.880", 
   "id": "s000122", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir behalten die Befristung als Mittel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.000", 
   "id": "s000123", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber eben grunds\u00e4tzlich mit einer Dauer von maximal 24\u00a0Monaten und darin maximal drei Verl\u00e4ngerungen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.720", 
   "id": "s000124", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dar\u00fcber hinaus geht nichts. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.120", 
   "id": "s000125", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es sei denn, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "281.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.280", 
   "id": "s000126", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
