  {
   "begin": "286.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.360", 
   "id": "s000129", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die n\u00f6tig sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "289.600", 
   "id": "s000130", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber diese Sonderregelungen m\u00fcssen eben die Ausnahme sein\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "289.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.760", 
   "id": "s000131", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und nicht die Regel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "293.440", 
   "id": "s000132", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es im Moment der Fall ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "293.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.200", 
   "id": "s000133", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie uns dar\u00fcber gemeinsam im Ausschuss diskutieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "297.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "302.520", 
   "id": "s000134", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie uns diesen vollst\u00e4ndigen Gesetzentwurf zur Basis einer Diskussion \u00fcber eine Reform, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "302.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "306.840", 
   "id": "s000135", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcber eine wirklich soziale Reform unserer befristeten Arbeitsverh\u00e4ltnisse machen. "
